<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Run Faster — Train Smart, Run Fast</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="styles.css" />
    <script defer src="script.js"></script>
</head>
<body>
    <header class="hero">
        <div class="container">
            <h1>Run Faster</h1>
            <p class="lead">Practical tips, drills, and a simple pace calculator to help you run as fast as possible.</p>
            <a class="btn" href="#training">Get a plan</a>
            <img class="hero-art" src="images/shoe.svg" alt="Running shoe illustration" />
        </div>
    </header>

    <main class="container">
        <section id="tips">
            <h2>Top Tips</h2>
            <ul>
                <li>Build speed with interval training: short repeats with recovery.</li>
                <li>Include strength work twice a week (hips, glutes, core).</li>
                <li>Prioritize consistent mileage and progressive overload.</li>
                <li>Recover: sleep, nutrition, and easy runs matter.</li>
                <li>Drill form: high knees, A-skips, and bounding to improve turnover.</li>
            </ul>
        </section>

        <section id="training">
            <h2>Sample 4-Week Speed Block</h2>
            <table>
                <thead>
                    <tr><th>Week</th><th>Key Workout</th><th>Notes</th></tr>
                </thead>
                <tbody>
                    <tr><td>1</td><td>6 x 400m @ 5K pace</td><td>Recover 90s</td></tr>
                    <tr><td>2</td><td>8 x 400m @ faster than 5K</td><td>Recover 90s</td></tr>
                    <tr><td>3</td><td>5 x 800m @ 5K pace</td><td>Recover 2-3min</td></tr>
                    <tr><td>4</td><td>Race-pace tune: 2K-3K effort</td><td>Sharpen and taper</td></tr>
                </tbody>
            </table>
        </section>

        <section id="drills">
            <h2>Speed Drills</h2>
            <div class="thumb-grid">
                <figure class="thumb"><img src="images/stopwatch.svg" alt="stopwatch icon"><figcaption>Hill sprints</figcaption></figure>
                <figure class="thumb"><img src="images/shoe.svg" alt="stride icon"><figcaption>Strides & drills</figcaption></figure>
                <figure class="thumb"><img src="images/stopwatch.svg" alt="plyo icon"><figcaption>Plyometrics</figcaption></figure>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section id="calculator">
            <h2>Pace Calculator</h2>
            <p>Enter distance and time to compute pace per kilometer.</p>
            <form id="paceForm">
                <label>Distance (km)
                    <input type="number" id="distance" min="0.1" step="0.01" value="5" required />
                </label>
                <label>Time (mm:ss)
                    <input type="text" id="time" placeholder="25:00" value="25:00" required />
                </label>
                <button type="submit" class="btn">Calculate</button>
            </form>
            <div id="result" aria-live="polite"></div>
        </section>
    </main>

    <footer>
        <div class="container">© Running Tips • Built for quick reference</div>
    </footer>
</body>
</html>
